[00:02.981]О тоска о битве
[00:05.547]Ведь война несёт покой
[00:11.615]Бьюсь за то, чего здесь нет.
[00:17.263]There’s not one road to get there,
[00:20.465]Its not just swing a sword or take it in you - oh no
[00:25.482]It’s what you’ve given, what has left your bones bare,
[00:29.582]It’s only then the path is yours to walk through
[00:34.346]Take the path to the end, and a monster you’ll find sleeping,
[00:38.165]Where the wounds cut deep in the earth are full of flowers,
[00:42.447]He sees not what you’ve lost, the judgement is fleeting
[00:46.549]Takes another sword, takes another sword, counts his hours…
[00:50.765]Some take their risks, by avoiding the fight
[00:54.823]It’s a right way to go if your wrong is your right,
[00:59.123]But I feel my duty and honor to act,
[01:03.456]take up in my harbor, and I’ll have your back.
