[01:33.474]Мои кости спят в полях,
[01:40.261]И не чувствуй эту боль.
[01:43.395]Oh oh oh
[01:49.962]Мои кости спят в полях,
[01:52.026]И не чувствуй эту боль.
[01:55.495]Your friends will bring you solace
[01:58.727]In a world where things feel edged to anger, Peace, through war
[02:03.927]To hold your ground and get there, is strength
[02:07.379]There’s a calm that stills the deepest hum of pain forgotten.
[02:11.678]Some think they’ll win just by poking the bear,
[02:15.744]It’s not the tip of your sword, that’s got me scared,
[02:20.145]Don’t take what you want then expect me to hide,
[02:24.562]I’ll cut long and deep, I’ll cut hard and wide.
